These events are no different from ones created by users. Ads will appear as suggestions for spontaneous planning that users will manipulate. Closed events between friends can be created, however, they can also be open to friends of friends which will facilitate exponential growth in attendance. Businesses will utilize Impulsiv to increase volume.
